name: Swilla Corey
Lore: 'Petty criminals throughout the galaxy often earn extra money by teaching their trade to intiates. Thievery has become more popular as the Empire tightens its grip.',
Text: 'Deploy on your non-thief to give that character thief skill. Once during each of your control phases, may target one device at same site. Draw destiny. If destiny < target''s destiny number, it is stolen. OR Deploy on a weapon to prevent theft. (Immune to Alter.)',
